YIDDISH ENGLISH.

5
00:00:39,567 --> 00:00:42,466
NOVEMBER FIVE, NINETEEN NINETY SIX.

6
00:00:42,466 --> 00:00:47,266
PHYLLIS DREAZEN INTERVIEWING SIMON MENTSHER, CHICAGO, ILLINOIS.

7
00:00:47,266 --> 00:00:49,449
WE'LL SPEAK IN YIDDISH AND ENGLISH.

8
00:00:50,856 --> 00:00:52,034
vi heystu?

9
00:00:52,257 --> 00:00:55,271
ikh heys Shimshen Mentsher ben Yosef.

10
00:00:56,998 --> 00:00:58,814
vi heystu in Amerike?

11
00:00:58,973 --> 00:01:01,498
in Amerike heys ikh SIMON Mentsher.

12
00:01:03,580 --> 00:01:05,453
un ven iz dayn geburtstog?

13
00:01:05,487 --> 00:01:08,535
mayn geburtstog iz may ELEVEN,

14
00:01:08,625 --> 00:01:10,441
toyznt nayn hundert tsvelef.

15
00:01:10,515 --> 00:01:12,436
un vi alt bistu yetst?

16
00:01:12,017 --> 00:01:13,648
ikh bin itstert alt

17
00:01:14,042 --> 00:01:16,753
akht, fir un akhtsik a helft.

18
00:01:17,306 --> 00:01:19,284
ver bistu geboyrn gevorn?

19
00:01:19,476 --> 00:01:23,655
ikh bin geboyrn gevorn dem eleftn may, nayntsn tsvelef.

20
00:01:23,323 --> 00:01:24,329
avu?

21
00:01:24,623 --> 00:01:27,081
in a dorf, Kosmatsh

22
00:01:27,238 --> 00:01:28,751
in di Karpatn,

23
00:01:29,348 --> 00:01:32,329
vu fun dem dorf iz shoyn mer keyn veg nisht gevezn.

24
00:01:32,385 --> 00:01:34,033
dos iz shoyn gevezn ende.

25
00:01:34,309 --> 00:01:37,728
vayl v- vayter iz shoyn geven grenets mit Rumenyen,

26
00:01:37,768 --> 00:01:39,905
mit Ungarn, Tshekhoslovakay.

27
00:01:40,266 --> 00:01:42,386
un s'iz geven groyse be- berg.

28
00:01:42,426 --> 00:01:45,693
keyn mashinen zenen nisht gevezn in yener tsayt,

29
00:01:45,818 --> 00:01:49,524
alts iz nor gevezn mit ferd oder tsu fus.

30
00:01:51,994 --> 00:01:53,304
a sheyn dorf,

31
00:01:53,428 --> 00:01:55,059
sheyne Karpatn.

32
00:01:54,812 --> 00:01:56,156
vifl mentshn?

33
00:01:56,247 --> 00:01:59,650
dort iz gevezn bay di zekhtsik mishpokhes yidishe.

34
00:02:00,195 --> 00:02:04,256
trots dem vos dos dorf iz gevezn shtark vayt fun a shtetele,

35
00:02:04,363 --> 00:02:06,095
ober di yidn hobn gehat

36
00:02:06,338 --> 00:02:08,256
yeder zayn arbet,

37
00:02:08,346 --> 00:02:11,445
yeder zayn baruf, basheftikung,

38
00:02:11,788 --> 00:02:13,233
un mentshn hobn gelebt.

39
00:02:13,257 --> 00:02:15,810
nisht lang, vayl Poyln iz antshtanen

40
00:02:15,810 --> 00:02:17,903
in toyznt nayn hundert tsvontsik.

41
00:02:17,903 --> 00:02:21,131
in toyznt nayn hundert nayn un draysik iz gevorn oys Poyln,

42
00:02:21,542 --> 00:02:23,561
iz in gantsn nayntsn yor.

43
00:02:23,972 --> 00:02:27,023
fun nayntsn tsvelef biz nayntsn tsvontsik

44
00:02:27,023 --> 00:02:30,379
iz dos gevezn nisht Poyln, iz dos gevezn AUSTRO-WĘGRY.

45
00:02:31,093 --> 00:02:33,804
in nayntsn tsvontsik iz dos gevorn Poyln,

46
00:02:33,861 --> 00:02:35,812
hot men es gerufn Kleyn-Poyln,

47
00:02:36,662 --> 00:02:38,529
oder Galitsyen,

48
00:02:38,923 --> 00:02:42,697
funem vort vayl s'iz geven a dorf Halitsh,

49
00:02:42,771 --> 00:02:46,168
un dort iz geven a a groyser mentsh, an ukrainer,

50
00:02:46,168 --> 00:02:49,531
hobn es di ukrainer gerufn HALICHINA

51
00:02:49,622 --> 00:02:51,973
un di estr-, austro-vengryer hobn gerufn

52
00:02:51,973 --> 00:02:53,159
GALIZIEN.

53
00:02:53,335 --> 00:02:57,041
un azoy iz dos gevorn in der yidisher shprakh, hot men gezogt "a galitsyaner".

54
00:02:57,621 --> 00:02:59,415
in Galitsyen geyt arayn:

55
00:02:59,415 --> 00:03:00,365
KRAKÓW,

56
00:03:00,523 --> 00:03:03,605
Tarnopol, Stanisloy un Lemberik.

57
00:03:03,966 --> 00:03:06,947
di fir voyevudstves zenen gevezn gerekhnt

58
00:03:07,003 --> 00:03:09,911
in Galitsyen. di iberike teyln fun Poyln

59
00:03:09,911 --> 00:03:11,722
zenen geven Tsentral-Poyln

60
00:03:11,914 --> 00:03:13,933
un andere teyln fun Poyln.

61
00:03:15,593 --> 00:03:18,827
dertseyl undz epes vegn dayn familye.

62
00:03:19,440 --> 00:03:21,965
ikh bin geboyrn ⟨in⟩ nayntsn tsvelef.

63
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:24,601
in nayntsn fertsn hot zikh ongehoybn

64
00:03:24,601 --> 00:03:26,285
di ershte velt-milkhome.

65
00:03:26,342 --> 00:03:28,361
bin ikh alt geven tsvey yor.

66
00:03:29,025 --> 00:03:32,869
mayn tate iz nisht a profesyonaler, ah, rebe,

67
00:03:32,869 --> 00:03:34,638
ober er hot gehat smikhe.

68
00:03:34,847 --> 00:03:37,625
hot men im in nayntsn fertsn di estraykher

69
00:03:37,750 --> 00:03:40,764
mobilizirt in der armey als rebe.

70
00:03:41,496 --> 00:03:43,771
un in der tsayt

71
00:03:43,771 --> 00:03:46,906
hobn di rusn gehat a groysn nitsokhn,

72
00:03:47,233 --> 00:03:50,647
un di estraykhishe armey hot opgetretn

73
00:03:50,647 --> 00:03:54,349
fun ire grenetsn zenen zey ariber biz der tshekhisher teritorye.

74
00:03:54,928 --> 00:03:56,474
un dortn

75
00:03:56,599 --> 00:04:03,377
hobn zey, zet oys, oyfgehaltn a bisl di rusn, ober mayn tate iz shver farvundet gevorn,

76
00:04:03,433 --> 00:04:06,970
un in shpitol iz er geshtorbn.

77
00:04:07,804 --> 00:04:11,100
mir zenen geblibn n- in der heym.

78
00:04:11,100 --> 00:04:14,379
un s'iz ge-, ale mentshn hobn zikh evakuirt,

79
00:04:14,487 --> 00:04:17,636
⟨nor⟩ vayl s'iz geven zeyer groyse milkhomes dortn.

80
00:04:18,047 --> 00:04:21,011
iz mayn mame ge⟨shtonen iber der letster tsayt⟩

81
00:04:21,067 --> 00:04:28,447
mit a groysn kestl kakao, mit, mit bulkelekh, vayl di yidn fun di shtetl⟨ekh zenen gegangen⟩ durkh undzer dorf

82
00:04:28,447 --> 00:04:29,988
kedey tsu antloyfn

83
00:04:30,163 --> 00:04:33,971
un in letstn moment hot zi genemen oyf a vogn mit a ferd

84
00:04:34,146 --> 00:04:37,110
un hot undz ale arayngezetst. ⟨zenen mir damolts⟩ gevezn

85
00:04:37,521 --> 00:04:39,618
finef meydlekh,

86
00:04:39,618 --> 00:04:41,244
un ikh bin geven eyner.

87
00:04:41,301 --> 00:04:43,219
du vilst zogn di nemen?

88
00:04:42,668 --> 00:04:45,609
yo. se, akhuts mir iz gevezn,

89
00:04:45,609 --> 00:04:47,960
di eltste shvester iz gevezn Dine,

90
00:04:48,490 --> 00:04:50,880
un di tsveyte nokh ir iz geven Roze,

91
00:04:50,886 --> 00:04:53,141
di drite iz gevezn Ester,

92
00:04:53,248 --> 00:04:56,957
un di letste tsvey Maynkele un Sorkele.

93
00:04:56,826 --> 00:04:57,900
un di...

94
00:04:56,957 --> 00:05:01,258
mer-veyniker a yor ⟨UNK⟩rikht, ober ikh gedenk nisht genoy.

95
00:05:01,534 --> 00:05:04,346
un ikh bin geven der yingster.

96
00:05:03,897 --> 00:05:05,140
di mame?

97
00:05:05,230 --> 00:05:07,249
di mame Khane,

98
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,611
hot gehey- Khane.

99
00:05:07,879 --> 00:05:12,540
di mame Khane. vi azoy iz mayn tate gekumen fun Tarnopoler voyevudstve

100
00:05:12,590 --> 00:05:14,490
keyn Stanislover in Karpatn,

101
00:05:14,490 --> 00:05:17,862
veys ikh nisht, vayl ikh bin dokh, ikh bin geven a kind.

102
00:05:17,869 --> 00:05:21,376
ober yedn fals, s'iz dray hundert kilometer a mehalekh

103
00:05:21,376 --> 00:05:23,837
fun dem ort vu mayn tate iz geboyrn gevorn.

104
00:05:24,062 --> 00:05:27,768
bay mayn mame's tsad iz gevezn nayn kinder,

105
00:05:28,011 --> 00:05:29,794
zin un tekhter.

106
00:05:29,952 --> 00:05:32,393
tate's tsad iz gevezn tsen,

107
00:05:32,787 --> 00:05:35,846
un ale zenen shoyn gevezn groyse,

108
00:05:35,846 --> 00:05:38,461
es iz shoyn gevezn fun di k- fun di kinder,

109
00:05:38,461 --> 00:05:41,133
fun di tekhter, fun di zin iz shoyn geven mishpokhes,

110
00:05:41,207 --> 00:05:42,883
un

111
00:05:42,883 --> 00:05:46,567
der tate hot gehat a groys hoyz oyfgeboyt.

112
00:05:46,911 --> 00:05:50,612
mit vos er hot zikh farnemen veys ikh nisht, nor mir hobn gehat zeyer a sakh

113
00:05:50,612 --> 00:05:51,968
shtiklekh feld.

114
00:05:52,294 --> 00:05:56,526
di Karpatn zenen dokh groyse berg. un dort vu s'iz do a shtikl glaykher plats,

115
00:05:56,526 --> 00:05:59,577
dort ken men boyen a hoyz oder farakern,

116
00:05:59,652 --> 00:06:03,578
vayl in Karpatn iz dos erd nisht keyn shvartse erd,

117
00:06:03,718 --> 00:06:05,652
nor s'iz gevezn

118
00:06:05,845 --> 00:06:08,134
 grintsayg,

119
00:06:08,207 --> 00:06:10,057
sades frukhtn.

120
00:06:10,705 --> 00:06:13,196
di ortshaft iz geven azoy sheyn,

121
00:06:13,422 --> 00:06:15,728
vayl s'iz gevezn bern,

122
00:06:16,273 --> 00:06:17,735
bure bern,

123
00:06:17,792 --> 00:06:21,144
velf iz zenen gantse stades ge- gevezn

124
00:06:21,167 --> 00:06:23,051
un vilde khazeyrim.

125
00:06:23,361 --> 00:06:27,678
un di p- di politsey di estraykhishe un di poylishe dernokh

126
00:06:27,678 --> 00:06:31,576
flegn trefn nor a shtikl in shikh, a shtikl fus.

127
00:06:31,576 --> 00:06:33,109
zey flegn iberfaln.

128
00:06:33,418 --> 00:06:38,272
un me hot nisht derloybt tsu m- tsu hargenen zey, tsu shi- tsu shisn,

129
00:06:38,363 --> 00:06:41,884
nor groyse mentshn hobn gekent yedes mol makhn

130
00:06:41,890 --> 00:06:45,039
polyevanye un un opshisn zey.

131
00:06:45,973 --> 00:06:48,279
di gegnt aleyn iz geven azoy sheyn,

132
00:06:48,420 --> 00:06:50,864
az a sakh mentshn hobn gezogt, az

133
00:06:50,864 --> 00:06:52,836
s'farglaykht zikh vi Shveytsaryen.

134
00:06:53,432 --> 00:06:55,130
un nisht gekukt deroyf

135
00:06:55,204 --> 00:06:57,934
vos di yidn zenen geven nisht keyn shtark raykhe,

136
00:06:57,934 --> 00:07:01,006
nor zey hobn gehat mer-veyniker di parnose: iz geven shusters,

137
00:07:01,006 --> 00:07:02,238
shnayders,

138
00:07:02,238 --> 00:07:03,604
zey hobn gehat gevelbn.

139
00:07:03,604 --> 00:07:06,329
un zeyer a sakh yidn hobn zikh take farnemen aleyn.

140
00:07:06,329 --> 00:07:07,967
zey hobn gehat gute sadn,

141
00:07:07,967 --> 00:07:10,337
un di frukhtn hobn zey gehat i zumer

142
00:07:10,337 --> 00:07:13,135
i osyen frukhtn un far vinter oykh.

143
00:07:13,378 --> 00:07:15,510
dermit flegn zey dos farkoyfn.

144
00:07:15,510 --> 00:07:18,286
itster flegn zey koyfn bay di ukrainer

145
00:07:18,286 --> 00:07:19,931
di beste gribes,

146
00:07:19,931 --> 00:07:21,542
MUSHROOMS.

147
00:07:21,542 --> 00:07:23,669
vayse, on eyn vorem

148
00:07:23,669 --> 00:07:26,538
iz ge-, flegn trikenen, zeyer fayne.

149
00:07:26,538 --> 00:07:29,471
flegn dos zeyer gut koyfn di groyse shtet,

150
00:07:29,578 --> 00:07:32,322
Varshe un Lodzh un Lemberik.

151
00:07:32,532 --> 00:07:36,660
itstert-o, ze-, di goyim flegn trikenen di frukhtn,

152
00:07:36,801 --> 00:07:39,244
un zey flegn es makhn zeyer sheyn un reyn.

153
00:07:39,244 --> 00:07:41,953
akhuts dem iz geven in der gegnt zeyer a sakh

154
00:07:41,953 --> 00:07:43,257
yagedes,

155
00:07:43,517 --> 00:07:45,927
dos heyst mali- malines,

156
00:07:45,927 --> 00:07:48,877
CHERNIKA, di... ofenes.

157
00:07:49,018 --> 00:07:53,225
un dos alts fleg men mit azelkhe feser

158
00:07:53,225 --> 00:07:54,297
hiltserne

159
00:07:54,297 --> 00:08:00,662
onlodn oyf a ferd tsvey feser azelkhe, un raytndik mitn ferd, vayl s'iz

160
00:08:00,662 --> 00:08:05,271
nisht gevezn keyn guter veg. nokh yedn regn iz der veg gevorn tse- tseveykt.

161
00:08:05,826 --> 00:08:10,792
di, di, di velder dortn zenen gevezn zeyer gute kvalitet.

162
00:08:10,792 --> 00:08:12,353
say di sosnes,

163
00:08:12,353 --> 00:08:13,784
say di bereze,

164
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:15,591
say buk,

165
00:08:15,681 --> 00:08:16,957
say dub,

166
00:08:17,284 --> 00:08:22,104
un di beste avyos, avyo-beryozn, avyo-sosne.

167
00:08:22,144 --> 00:08:25,018
fleg men nisht megn hakn

168
00:08:25,018 --> 00:08:27,250
on der erloybenish funem LEŚNICZY.

169
00:08:27,392 --> 00:08:30,778
oyb der LEŚNICZY hot erloybt, hot men gemegt oyshakn a bisl f-

170
00:08:30,801 --> 00:08:33,514
beymer kedey makhn a remont funem hoyz.

171
00:08:33,514 --> 00:08:36,667
ober on an erloybenish hot men gornisht getort t- tun.

172
00:08:38,125 --> 00:08:42,500
akhuts dem iz di mentshn,

173
00:08:42,500 --> 00:08:45,847
zey hobn, zenen gevezn zeyer, di yidn,

174
00:08:45,887 --> 00:08:47,585
frayndlekh tsu zikh.

175
00:08:47,710 --> 00:08:54,015
un khotsh dos dorf iz gevezn tsevorfn, fun a hoyz biz a hoyz iz geven hundert un tsvey hundert meter a mol,

176
00:08:54,190 --> 00:08:56,918
nor di, iz geven tsvey shiln.

177
00:08:57,430 --> 00:09:00,683
un, s'iz nisht geven ⟨a⟩ shnayder-shil oder

178
00:09:00,683 --> 00:09:04,185
oder andere oder a kloyz epes, proste shiln, vi in a dorf,

179
00:09:04,185 --> 00:09:06,013
oysgeboyt fun holts.

180
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:09,180
in dorf iz gevezn di melamdim,

181
00:09:09,180 --> 00:09:13,348
vos hobn gelernt dem tsu ershtn dem alef-beys

182
00:09:13,348 --> 00:09:14,740
un dernokh davenen.

183
00:09:14,740 --> 00:09:18,990
un a a bisl hot men ongehoybn tsu lernen shoyn afile khumesh un Rashe.

184
00:09:19,063 --> 00:09:22,528
un, nor di ale yidn, trots dem

185
00:09:22,528 --> 00:09:25,976
vos zey zenen geven draysik-fertsik kilometer fun a shtetele,

186
00:09:26,067 --> 00:09:29,886
un keyn beys-oylem iz nisht gevezn dortn. flegn, az se fleg shtarbn a yid,

187
00:09:29,886 --> 00:09:31,767
fleg men firn mit a vogn

188
00:09:31,767 --> 00:09:34,492
tsvelf kilometer, fuftsn kilometer.

189
00:09:34,492 --> 00:09:36,911
tsvey kilometer, dakht zikh mir, iz a mayl.

190
00:09:37,390 --> 00:09:42,564
un di un di yidn zenen gevezn genug baleznt.

191
00:09:42,705 --> 00:09:46,768
in Poyln, iz afile in aza min dorf farvarfn,

192
00:09:46,768 --> 00:09:49,195
iz gevezn a Tarbut-shul

193
00:09:49,607 --> 00:09:51,069
un a yidishe shul,

194
00:09:51,396 --> 00:09:53,094
un der melamed hot gelernt.

195
00:09:53,168 --> 00:09:56,587
di eltern vos zey zenen gevezn farmeglekh flegn shikn di kinder

196
00:09:56,678 --> 00:09:59,794
in in shtetlekh oder in shtet.

197
00:10:00,154 --> 00:10:02,476
di noentste shtot iz gevezn Kolomey.

198
00:10:02,483 --> 00:10:07,711
di hoyptshtot iz gevezn, di di oblast, di voyevudstve iz geven Stanisloy.

199
00:10:07,711 --> 00:10:10,166
nor Kolomey iz gevezn merer

200
00:10:10,166 --> 00:10:17,006
merer mit miskher, vayl s'iz gevezn, fun Kolomey keyn Stanisloy iz geven zeyer vayt.

201
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:19,084
flegn kumen di hutsuln,

202
00:10:19,084 --> 00:10:21,089
di ukrainer hot men gerufn di hutsuln.

203
00:10:21,197 --> 00:10:22,518
flegn kumen

204
00:10:22,518 --> 00:10:25,185
ahin un ⟨UNK⟩ ⟨oysfar⟩koyfn, azoy

205
00:10:25,185 --> 00:10:28,143
der groyser miskher tsvishn yidn fun di derfer.

206
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:30,939
geven etlekhe un draysik derfer leng-oys

207
00:10:30,939 --> 00:10:34,016
der rumenisher, tshekhisher un ungerisher grenets.

208
00:10:34,748 --> 00:10:39,427
s'iz nisht keyn fele, az yidn zol zikh mishn mit andere felker.

209
00:10:39,427 --> 00:10:41,545
yidn mit yidn hobn khasene gehat.

210
00:10:41,545 --> 00:10:44,124
moral iz gevezn genug hoykh.

211
00:10:44,383 --> 00:10:47,679
un s'iz geven yidishe organizatsyes.

212
00:10:47,679 --> 00:10:53,067
nor in di derfer flegn zayn merstn teyl stam sionistishe organizatsyes.

213
00:10:53,091 --> 00:10:54,936
HANOAR HATSIYONI,

214
00:10:54,936 --> 00:10:57,914
ober nisht di linke. geven HASHOMER HATSAIR,

215
00:10:57,914 --> 00:11:00,577
linke Poletsiyen, rekhte Poletsiyen,

216
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:03,614
di GORDONIA, di iberike, dos iz shoyn geven ⟨in⟩ di shtetlekh.

217
00:11:04,937 --> 00:11:06,703
MIZRAKHI gevezn, yo.

